Name: Valentino Rossi The Game Compact
About the game: Valentino Rossi The Game Compact enables you to choose all the official riders, teams and tracks in the 2016 MotoGP™ season. Various game modes available: Quick Race, Championship and Split Screen, as well as 5 legendary events which have come to exemplify the 9-time world champion’s career!
